<div id="CW_Company_Profile_Mid_336x280" oldstyle=""><script type='text/javascript'> googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display('CW_Company_Profile_Mid_336x280'); }); </script></div>        </div>
    <div class="span8">
        <div class="profile-item lg">
            <h4><span class="ico-vcard ico-blue"></span>Overview of Ventas, Inc. in Louisville, KY</h4>
            <div id="profile-text">
                 <p> Ventas, Inc. filed as a <b>Foreign for Profit Corporation</b> in the <b>State of Florida</b> on Friday, June 28, 1991 and is approximately twenty-four years old, as recorded in documents filed with <b>Florida Department of State</b>. The filing is <b>currently active</b> as of the last data refresh which occured on Sunday, June 7, 2015. A corporate filing is called a foreign filing when an existing corporate entity files in a state other than the state they originally filed in. This does not necessarily mean that they are from outside the United States. </p> <div> <h4>Key People</h4> <p> <a href="/Kentucky/Louisville/brian-k-wood-P5885290.aspx">Brian Wood</a> serves as the <b>Secretary</b> and has interests in other corporate entities including <a href="/Kentucky/Louisville/ventas-mob-holdings-llc-2524438.aspx">Ventas Mob Holdings, LLC</a>, <a href="/Kentucky/Louisville/vtr-emrts-holdings-llc/26672353.aspx">Vtr-Emrts Holdings, LLC</a> , and <a href="/Kentucky/Louisville/pslt-als-properties-iii-llc/26720522.aspx">Pslt-Als Properties III, LLC</a> . </p> <p> <a href="/Kentucky/Louisville/ronald-geary-8326786.aspx">Ronald Geary</a> is the <b>Director</b> of Ventas, Inc.. Ronald&#39;s additional corporate interests include <a href="/Texas/Houston/ce-king-plaza-inc/37062735.aspx">C.E. King Plaza, Inc.</a>, <a href="/Kentucky/Louisville/res-care-inc-2818836.aspx">Res-Care, Inc.</a> , and <a href="/Kentucky/Louisville/res-care-florida-inc-3013450.aspx">Res-Care Florida, Inc.</a> Ronald's past corporate affiliations include <a href="/Kentucky/Louisville/arbor-inc/41483147.aspx">Arbor, Inc.</a>, <a href="/Kentucky/Louisville/alternative-youth-services-inc/42964778.aspx">Alternative Youth Services, Inc.</a> and four others. </p> <p> The Director of Ventas, Inc. is <a href="/Illinois/Chicago/douglas-crocker-P6331709.aspx">Douglas Crocker</a>. . Douglas has other corporate interests including <a href="/Illinois/Chicago/eqr-fielders-crossing-gp-llc/30270769.aspx">Eqr-Fielders Crossing Gp, LLC</a> located in Chicago, IL . Douglas's past corporate affiliations include <a href="/Illinois/Chicago/first-capital-financial-corporation-2807093.aspx">First Capital Financial Corporation</a>, <a href="/Illinois/Chicago/first-capital-investment-corporation-which-will-do-business/40827392.aspx">First Capital Investment Corporation, Which Will DO Business In California As, Florida First Capital Investment Corporation</a> and six others. </p> <p> The registered agent for the company is Ct Corporation System. Also known as a statutory or resident agent, the registered agent is responsible for receiving legal notifications regarding court summons, lawsuits, and other legal actions involving the corporate entity. </p> </div> 
